trans-unit.source: Represents a single row delete operation expressed as a command tree.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma operação de eliminação de linha única expressada como uma árvore de comandos.
Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"></xref> that specifies the predicate used to determine which members of the target collection should be deleted.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"> </xref> que especifica o predicado utilizado para determinar quais os membros da coleção de destino devem ser eliminados.

trans-unit.source: The predicate can include only the following elements: <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbComparisonExpression> (represents equality), <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbConstantExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbIsNullExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbPropertyExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbVariableReferenceExpression> (references the target), <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbAndExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbOrExpression>, and <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbNotExpression>.
trans-unit.target: O predicado pode incluir apenas os seguintes elementos: <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbComparisonExpression>(representa igualdade), <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbConstantExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbIsNullExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbPropertyExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbVariableReferenceExpression>(referencia o destino), <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbAndExpression>, <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbOrExpression>e <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbNotExpression>.</xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbNotExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbOrExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbAndExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbVariableReferenceExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbPropertyExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbIsNullExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbConstantExpression> </xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbComparisonExpression>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"></xref> that specifies the predicate used to determine which members of the target collection should be deleted.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"> </xref> que especifica o predicado utilizado para determinar quais os membros da coleção de destino devem ser eliminados.
